# Workflow Software for Notifications - MagicBell
created: undefined, last updated: 2026-06-02, [Read more](https://www.magicbell.com/workflows)

Broadcast notifications to users via Slack, Email, SMS, and more.
Configure channel-specific formatting and delivery options.
...
POST /broadcasts
{
"title": "New order received",
"recipients": [{"email": "[email protected]"}],
"overrides": {
"providers": {
"slack": {
"blocks": [{"type": "section", "text": {"type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*Order #1234* confirmed"}}]
}
...
Send transactional emails via SMTP, SendGrid, Mailgun, or Amazon SES.
...
